   Bayik, Caglar; Alpat, Mert; Bektas, Meric, Zonguldak Bulent Ecevit Univ, Dept Geomat Engn, Zonguldak, Turkiye.
   Esetlili, Mustafa Tolga; Kurucu, Yusuf, Ege Univ, Dept Soil Sci \& Plant Nutr, Izmir, Turkiye.
   Ustuner, Mustafa, Samsun Univ, Dept Climate Sci \& Meteorol Engn, Samsun, Turkiye.
   Sanli, Fusun Balik, Yildiz Tech Univ, Dept Geomat Engn, Istanbul, Turkiye.},
