   Sheng, Yinsheng; Xu, Xinpeng; Ding, Wencheng; He, Ping, Chinese Acad Agr Sci, Inst Agr Resources \& Reg Planning, State Key Lab Efficient Utilizat Arid \& Semiarid, Beijing 100081, Peoples R China.
   Sheng, Yinsheng, Jilin Agr Univ, Coll Resources \& Environm, Changchun 130118, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.jclepro.2023.139739},
EarlyAccessDate = {NOV 2023},
Article-Number = {139739},
