   Ofem, Kokei Ikpi; Okon, Paul Bassey; Isong, Isong Abraham, Univ Calabar, Fac Agr Forestry \& Wildlife Resources Management, Dept Soil Sci, PMB 1115,Etta Agbo Rd, Calabar 540004, Nigeria.
   Qin, Chengzhi, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Geog Sci \& Nat Resources Res, State Key Lab Resources \& Environm Informat Syst, Beijing 100101, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.iswcr.2021.11.003},
