   CONFERENCE ON ELECTRICAL AND COMPUTER ENGINEERING (WIECON-ECE 2020)},
Year = {2020},
Pages = {410-413},
Abstract = {The stochastic nature of photovoltaic (PV) power generation can have
   significant impacts on the power grid stability and reliability. Hence,
   it is essential to have an accurate forecasting of the PV power
   generation. In this paper, a new machine learning (ML) framework is
